<doc id="1118960" wikidata="Q111606" url="?curid=1118960" title="Roccafranca">
<text>Roccafranca (Brescian: ) is a comune in the province of Brescia, in Lombardy, northern Italy. It is located on the left bank of the Oglio River, in the Po Plain.

