<doc id="1118993" wikidata="Q111639" url="?curid=1118993" title="Rovato">
<text>Rovato (Brescian: ) is a &quot;comune&quot; in the province of Brescia, in Lombardy, northern Italy. Neighbouring towns are Coccaglio, Erbusco and Cazzago San Martino. It is located in the Franciacorta hills, 11 km south of Lake Iseo and 18 km west of Brescia.

==Transport==
* Rovato railway station
* Rovato Borgo railway station
* Rovato Città railway station

